        "custom_css": ".elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title {\n  color: #1f365c;\n}\n\n.elementor-widget-heading h1.elementor-heading-title { font-size: 42px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; }\n.elementor-widget-heading h2.elementor-heading-title { font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; }\n.elementor-widget-heading h3.elementor-heading-title { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 700; }\n.elementor-widget-heading h4.elementor-heading-title { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 700; }\n\n/* Body text size — match fsi-event-styles.php p baseline (17px / 1.6) so cards + paragraphs read at the same weight as the WPBakery LLSS page. The kit Text token (14px) is too small for body content. */\n.elementor-widget-text-editor p,\n.elementor-widget-text-editor li {\n  font-size: 17px;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n/* Slightly tighter at mobile */\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .elementor-widget-text-editor p,\n  .elementor-widget-text-editor li {\n    font-size: 16px;\n  }\n}",
